first_para: Atta-Ur-Rehman Chishti known as Rehman Chishti رحمن چشتی (born 4 October 1978) is a British Conservative politician who was elected MP for Gillingham and Rainham in the 2010 general election.

full.extract: Atta-Ur-Rehman Chishti known as Rehman Chishti رحمن چشتی (born 4 October 1978) is a British Conservative politician who was elected MP for Gillingham and Rainham in the 2010 general election.
full.title: Rehman Chishti
